data.text:
-> UKPSC RO ARO Revised Vacancy has been released.

-> In the direct recruitment for Review Officer/Assistant Review Officer Examination-2023, in which 08 vacant posts of Review Officer for Uttarakhand Public Service Commission were advertised at serial number 02 of the table has been modified to 07 posts.

-> The total vacancy now stands at 136 vacancies for the RO and ARO posts.

-> The Mains Exam will be held on 26th & 27th October 2024.

-> The Prelims was held on 17th December 2023.

-> The selection process includes a Preliminary Exam, Mains Exam, and Practical Test (Computer Proficiency and Typing).
